match_description: Dev, designer, and PM with complementary skills team up to build a project under a deadline.

profiles.raw_input: Hi everyone, I'm Alex Rivera, a full-stack developer specializing in React, Node.js, and TypeScript. I'm looking for a designer and project manager to join me for the upcoming hackathon. I have plenty of backend and frontend experience but need help with UI/UX and project coordination to build something amazing under the tight deadline!

roles.title: Senior Developer
highlights: Built multiple production applications from scratch
Lead developer on company's flagship product

profiles.extra_notes: I have a solid idea for a project that could win the hackathon, but need a designer and PM to complete the team. Looking to build a working prototype in 48 hours.

profiles.raw_input: Hello! I'm Jamie Chen, a Product Manager with UX/UI design skills. I've managed multiple projects with tight deadlines and love the energy of hackathons. Currently searching for a developer to team up with for the upcoming hackathon. I can handle project planning, feature prioritization, and help with design, but need someone who can implement the code efficiently under pressure!
